  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Warpriest Blessing</strong><br/><br/><p><b>Deities: </b>Erastil, Gozreh.</p><p><b>Creeping Vines (minor): </b>At 1st level, upon hitting with a melee attack, as a swift action you cause the creature you hit to sprout entangling vines that attempt to hold it in place, entangling it for 1 round (Reflex negates).</p><p><b>Battle Companion (major): </b>At 10th level, you can summon a battle companion. This ability functions as summon nature's ally IV, with a duration of 1 minute. This ability can summon only one animal, regardless of the list used, and the creature's type changes to plant instead of animal. For every 2 levels beyond 10th, the level of the summon nature's ally spell increases by 1, to a maximum of summon nature's ally IX at 20th level.</p>",
